(239, 1, '2012-04-24 12:24:53', '2012-04-24 06:54:53', 'CometChat Desktop Messenger is now out of beta and supports all popular CometChat plugins! Say hello to the Skype equivalent exclusively for your site users.\n\n<h2>Key Updates</h2>\n\n<strong>Voice, video, text chat directly from your desktop</strong>\n\nHave you imagined providing a Skype-like tool just for your site users? It''s all possible with the brand new CometChat Desktop Messenger! The Desktop Messenger allows your users to login and voice/video/text chat directly from their desktop. It runs on both- Windows and Mac OS.\n\n<strong>Support for all our popular plugins</strong>\n\nOur desktop messenger supports all popular plugins for CometChat including voice/video chat, whiteboard, writeboard, handwriting, block user, chat history and file sharing.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/04/pic2.png" alt="" title="File sharing with CometChat Messenger" width="600" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-244" />\n\n<strong>Enhancements and tweaks</strong>\n\nLanguage and theme files are now stored on your server so you can directly modify the look and feel quickly. New caching techniques have been implemented to reduce load times and bandwidth usage.\n\n<strong>White-labelled (Branding free)</strong>\n\nEvery purchase includes branding of the desktop messenger to match your site (icon, logo and name). Your users will never know that they are using CometChat.\n\n<h2>Purchase</h2>\n\n<a href="http://g.cometchat.com/AAsv89" target="_blank">Purchase CometChat Desktop Messenger</a> for your site. Note, you must have CometChat (any edition) installed on your site.\n\nFeel free to <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/contact">email us</a> if you have any questions.', 'Desktop Messenger graduates out of beta!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'desktop-messenger-graduates-out-of-beta', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:23:33', '2013-09-25 11:23:33', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/blog/?p=239', 0, 'post', '', 0),
