(270, 1, '2012-06-05 10:37:46', '2012-06-05 05:07:46', '<a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/cometchattv" title="CometChatTV" target="_blank"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/06/cometchattv.jpg" alt="" title="cometchattv" width="640" height="150" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-284" /></a>\n\nWe are happy to announce the launch of our new Youtube channel - <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/cometchattv" title="CometChatTV" target="_blank"><strong>CometChatTV</strong></a>!\n\nHaving a tough time understanding CometChat? Don''t get confused; CometChat enables your site users to chat with each other and their social networking friends in real-time. <strong>Check out our new introduction video.</strong>\n\n\n\nNeed to understand a particular feature? Now learn how to use CometChat with our new video tutorials. Our desktop messenger tutorial is guaranteed to get you excited!\n\n\n\nView all our videos at our new <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/cometchattv" title="CometChatTV" target="_blank">Youtube Channel</a> or subscribe to stay informed of all our latest videos.\n\n<a href="//www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user_id=Wu7LtG16A9ZgcyBpNMCX0Q&amp;feature=creators_cornier-//s.ytimg.com/yt/img/creators_corner/Subscribe_to_my_videos/YT_Subscribe_160x27_red.png"><img src="//s.ytimg.com/yt/img/creators_corner/Subscribe_to_my_videos/YT_Subscribe_160x27_red.png" style="border:0px" alt="Subscribe to me on YouTube" /></a>', 'New video tutorials and tour!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'new-video-tutorials-and-tour', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:23:33', '2013-09-25 11:23:33', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/blog/?p=270', 0, 'post', '', 0),
