(481, 1, '2012-11-27 11:41:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<h2> CometChat for WoltLab </h2>\n\nWoltLab is an interactive forum builder that uses a powerful forum software called Burning Board. Burning Board is a modern discussion platform that has a host of flexible features like extensive accessibility, moderation, privacy settings, user profiles, easy administration, customization, statistics and many more.\n\nCometChat integrates with WoltLab seamlessly to take this extensive usability over Burning Board forums to a whole new level.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/WoltLab.png" alt="" />\n\n- A strong community builder like WoltLab requires its users to stay connected whenever they want. Cometchat''s WebApp does just that! Available on all     the leading iOS and Android  devices CometChat  WebApp gives WoltLab users 24x7 access to their forums from absolutely anywhere.\n- Also active features like Chatrooms, Audio Video chats and Writeboard take WoltLab interactivity a notch higher.\n- CometChat Announcements, Screensharing, Collaborative documents and over 10,000+ single and multi-player games is a perfect recipe to any successful forum builder.\n- Users will be automatically logged into CometChat when they login to your WoltLab site.\n- CometChat will automatically show friends in the Who’s Online list.\n- Your users'' avatar and profile links are automatically integrated with CometChat.', 'New WoltLab integration for CometChat', '', 'pending', 'closed', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:23:31', '2013-09-25 11:23:31', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/blog/?p=481', 0, 'post', '', 0),
