(788, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:42', '2013-09-25 11:22:42', 'With a horde of some really impressive features, CometChat v5.0 is set to spread its charm all over again!\n\n<h2>CometChat App now available for iOS and Android</h2>\n\nBy the end of 2013, mobile phones will overtake desktops as the most commonly used device to access the web. Mobile traffic has increased by 75 percent and the demand for mobile increased by 167 percent. Are you following the trend?\n\nCometChat''s webapp in v4.6 was clearly a winner that kept users glued to your website from virtually everywhere! Inspired by our very own webapp, CometChat''s all new native app is here to let your users keep in touch like never before. Available on the Apple and Google Play stores, this app provides an aesthetically designed user interface that makes it an absolute delight to use. The CometChat app breaks all the barriers in mobile communication leaving no room for a missed conversation!\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/02/cometchatapp.png" alt="" title="cometchatapp" width="650" height="440" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-526" />\n\nOur apps can be used <strong>free of charge for any site</strong> running CometChat 5+. In the login screen, simply change the domain from "cometchat.com" to "yoursite.com" and start chatting!\n\n<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/ca/app/cometchat/id594110077" target="_blank"><img style="border:0" src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/02/applestore.png" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-536" /></a> &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.inscripts.cometchat" target="_blank"><img style="border:0" src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/02/googleplay.png" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-536" /></a>\n\n<em>Key features</em>\n\n* Auto-magically integrates with your site login\n* Can be used seamlessly with CometChat on your site\n* Text chat for both chatrooms and one-on-one\n* Smileys and handwriting support\n\nTo demo the app, enter the following details-\n\nSite: cometchat.com\nUsername: demo\nPassword: demo\n\n<strong><em>Would you like your own white-labelled app in the Apple/Google store?</em></strong>\n\nDon''t want your users to download the "CometChat" app? We are also providing completely white-labelled apps that can be added to Google Play and Apple stores. These apps can be purchased separately (includes both iOS and Android app) and come with complete white-labelling i.e. colors, logo, icon and name to match your site. So your site will have it''s own messenger app similar to the CometChat messenger but with your branding! It''s time to start competing with the big-wigs like Facebook Messenger! You can also charge for your mobile apps; so make money with every download!\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/02/whitelabelapps.jpg" width="650" height="440" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-560" />\n\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/contact">Contact us</a> for more details for your very own white-labelled chat app!\n\n<br />\n\n<h2>Wait, that''s not it. There''s more!</h2>\n\n<strong>Skype-like HD video quality</strong>\n\nNow add even higher quality audio and video chat to your site! CometChat and AddLive have teamed up to provide you with a no-flash solution for video communication. \n\nAccess the highest quality audio and video technology that constantly optimizes itself with every user''s experience. AddLive is providing 10,000 free minutes to all CometChat sites! Not interested in paying additional? No problem, you can always use our default audio/video chat component which is free of additional charge.   \n\n<strong>Broadcast yourself</strong>\n\nCometChat v5.0 provides your website users with the next best thing to having in-person meetings - broadcasting! With the new Broadcast plugin, users can conduct intensive audio/video broadcast meetings in no time. A user can start his/her broadcast from chatrooms and one-on-one conversations and begin one-way conversations with the other users. So the next time your users need to host a meeting, a few clicks is all they need to do!\n\n<strong>Custom guest names</strong>\n\nAre your guests tired of identifying themselves with numbers? v5 allows guests to change their name. No longer will they be known as "Guest 35634", "Guest 9634" etc. Let them choose their name (although the word "Guest" will be pre-fixed so that your users do not confuse them with members) like "Guest John", "Guest Jennifer" etc.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/02/guestnames.png" alt="" title="guestnames" width="650" height="440" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-528" />\n\n<strong>Mobile tab for your site</strong>\n\nUsing the new CometChat Mobile Tab extension, users don''t have to visit the webapp continuously to check if there is a new message. While browsing your site using their mobile devices, users will receive notification if there is a new message. A simple click sends your users to the CometChat mobile webapp directly.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/02/mobiletab.png" alt="" title="mobiletab" width="650" height="440" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-529" />\n\n<strong>Quicker Gtalk chat login</strong>\n\nYour users no longer need to login by manually entering their Google username and password to chat with their Gtalk friends. Using the more secure and trusted Google Auth technology, they are automatically redirected to Google''s site for a one-time login.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2013/02/googletalk.jpg" alt="" title="Google Auth Direct Login" width="650" height="310" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-563" />\n\n<strong>Miscellaneous enhancements and bug fixes</strong>\n\nHundreds of fixes have been performed in this release to ensure a smoother chatting experience. Manage blocked users feature has been added to light-weight chat mode as well. Ability to view chatroom logs and banning users by IP are just some of the new features in administration panel. Language and theme colors of mobile web-app, mobile native-app and desktop messenger can be now modified directly from the control panel as well. \n\n<br />\n\n<h2>Get CometChat v5.0!</h2>\n\nLoaded with brand new features and enhancements, CometChat v5.0 is a must for every site! \n\nWhat are you waiting for? <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/buy" title="Buy CometChat">Purchase CometChat today!</a> or <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/contact" title="Contact us">contact us</a> if you have any questions. \n\nAlready have CometChat? <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/my" title="Download CometChat">Download CometChat</a> or purchase our <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/my" title="Purchase Installation Service">installation service</a> if you would like us to perform the upgrade.', 'CometChat v5 - The best reloaded', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '525-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:42', '2013-09-25 11:22:42', '', 525, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/525-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(789, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '<strong>Security Update: 10th February 2013</strong>\n\nA security evaluation has revealed a critical security issue and we are releasing a patch for this issue.\n\n<strong>Instructions</strong>\n\nWe are providing a patch for CometChat versions 4.6, 4.4 and 4.0. Version If you are running a version less than 4.0 you should upgrade to get this and other security enhancements.\n\n<strong>Patching</strong>\n\n1. Identify the version of CometChat you are running (check cometchat/VERSION.txt file).\n2. Download and unzip the appropriate patch file below that matches your version.\n3. Upload the contents of the zip to your "cometchat" directory overwriting the existing files.\n\n<strong>Download</strong>\n\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/extra/130210_460.zip">Version 4.6 Patch</a>\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/extra/130210_440.zip">Version 4.4 Patch</a>\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/extra/130210_400.zip">Version 4.0 Patch</a>\n\n<strong>Notes</strong>\n\nOur software packages available from members area have already been updated with this security update.', 'CometChat Critical Security Update', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '508-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '', 508, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/508-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(790, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '<strong>Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year!</strong>\n\nAs the year approaches to an end, we celebrate and thank you! We''re incredibly grateful and humbled that you''ve selected CometChat to be an integral part of your site.\n\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/buy"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/12/happy2013.jpg" alt="" title="Happy Holidays!" width="600" height="600" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-503" /></a>\n\nCometChat has a come a long way in the last 4 years. We are constantly working on new features and have received a tremendous response for our latest version (v4.6). We have an interesting line-up of exciting enhancements in the coming year! So stay tuned and keep chatting...\n\nTo make this holiday season even more jolly, here is a 20% discount on any purchase (including upgrades!)\n\n<strong>Coupon Code: HAPPYHOLIDAYS\nValidity: Till 31st December</strong>\n\nSo what are you waiting for? <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/buy">Purchase</a> or <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/my">upgrade to a higher edition</a> of CometChat today!', 'Happy Holidays!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '499-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '', 499, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/499-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(791, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '<h2> CometChat for WoltLab </h2>\n\nWoltLab is an interactive forum builder that uses a powerful forum software called Burning Board. Burning Board is a modern discussion platform that has a host of flexible features like extensive accessibility, moderation, privacy settings, user profiles, easy administration, customization, statistics and many more.\n\nCometChat integrates with WoltLab seamlessly to take this extensive usability over Burning Board forums to a whole new level.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/WoltLab.png" alt="" />\n\n- A strong community builder like WoltLab requires its users to stay connected whenever they want. Cometchat''s WebApp does just that! Available on all     the leading iOS and Android  devices CometChat  WebApp gives WoltLab users 24x7 access to their forums from absolutely anywhere.\n- Also active features like Chatrooms, Audio Video chats and Writeboard take WoltLab interactivity a notch higher.\n- CometChat Announcements, Screensharing, Collaborative documents and over 10,000+ single and multi-player games is a perfect recipe to any successful forum builder.\n- Users will be automatically logged into CometChat when they login to your WoltLab site.\n- CometChat will automatically show friends in the Who’s Online list.\n- Your users'' avatar and profile links are automatically integrated with CometChat.', 'New WoltLab integration for CometChat', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '481-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '', 481, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/481-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(792, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '<h2> CometChat for Offiria </h2> \n\nOffiria is a private and secure social network for offices that offers collaborative and knowledge sharing features like real-time business streaming, profile management, community management, file and media sharing, project management, event management and many more.\n\nCometChat makes Offiria''s power of sharing even better by seamlessly integrating with it.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/Offiria.png" alt="" />\n\n- With features like Writeboard, Moderated Chatrooms, Audio/Video chats and File sharing, CometChat couldn''t be a  better match for Offiria.\n- CometChat provides a host of collaborative, fast and interactive tools like Announcements that help Offiria effortlessly run your business.\n- CometChat''s flawless compatibility with leading iOS and Android devices gives Offiria complete portability and makes them a match made in heaven.\n- Users will be automatically logged into CometChat when they login to your Offiria site.\n- CometChat will automatically show friends in the Who’s Online list.\n- CometChat will integrate with your user''s avatar and profile links as well.\n\n<h2> Cometchat for PG Dating Pro </h2>\n\nPG Dating Pro is turnkey PHP dating software to start internet dating service.This fully featured flexible community builder for romantic, matrimonial, casual, niche &amp; social dating matches any business idea. Fully equipped with communication tools like IM, chats, photo/videos galleries, groups, easy management areas, searches and SEO services make PG Dating Pro a powerful internet dating service. \n\nCometChat easily integrates with PG Dating Pro and adds a bunch of exciting features that help the users of PG Dating Pro connect more easily than ever.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/Dating_pro.png" alt="" />\n\n- CometChat takes connections to a whole new level with Translate module that translates real time conversations and makes sure that boundaries are no longer an issue.\n- Audio/Video chats, Multi-player games and Whiteboards make PG Dating pro an exciting platform for meeting new people and building relationships.\n- With CometChat''s new WebApp users can stay connected from anywhere which makes relationships build over this open-source dating software even more special.\n- Once a user logs into your PG Dating Pro site, he is automatically logged into CometChat too.\n- Users will be able to see their online friends in the Who''s Online list.\n- Your users'' avatar and profile links are automatically integrated with CometChat.\n\n <h2> CometChat for PG SocialBizz </h2>\n\nPG SocialBiz is PHP social networking software to quickly start your own social network, build your brand &amp; network with clients, friends &amp; followers.This is a professional community building software with comprehensive structure and attractive design. It has everything you need to launch fast chats, profiles, searches, services, payments and much more!\n\nCometChat seamlessly integrates with PG SocialBizz and adds a whole new set of interactive features to this Community builder.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/Social_Bizz.png" alt="" />\n\n- CometChat WebApp makes this Social Network builder absolutely portable by letting users stay connected from anywhere and anytime.\n- With over 10,000+ single and multi-player games CometChat keeps the users of PG SocialBizz glued to their site.\n- Chatrooms, Audio/Video chats, Chat history definitely gives this Social Networking software an edge over the others.\n- Users when login to your PG SocialBizz site, are automatically logged into CometChat. \n- Online friends will be visible to the users in the Who''s Online list.\n- The profile links and avatar chosen by your user will be integrated with CometChat.\n\n\n', 'New Offiria, PG Dating Pro and PG SocialBizz seamless integrations for CometChat! ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '435-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '', 435, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/435-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(793, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', 'If you loved CometChat v4.4, then get ready to be blown away by the breathtaking features of our latest and the most stylish version yet. Yes, CometChat v4.6 is here!\n\nWe’ve made the features you love, even more powerful!\n\n<h2>What’s new?</h2>\n\n<strong>Mobile Webapp</strong>\n\nWe are thrilled to announce the addition of the newest member to the CometChat family! Available on all the leading Android and iOS devices, this webapp lets you have CometChat in your pocket, literally! Make sure your users stay glued to your site, no matter where they are! Launch chatrooms and one-on-one chats from anywhere. With this beautifully designed webapp, your users will not miss another conversation or another smile.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/WebApp.png" alt="" />\n\n<strong>Chatrooms, now with the much awaited moderation feature!</strong>\n\n<strong>1. Kick first time offenders</strong>\n\nKick is the latest and probably one of the loudest chatroom features in version 4.6. It lets chatroom owners and moderators simply kick out another user from a chatroom. They can use kick to drop a hint to annoying users before banning them permanently.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/Kick.png" alt="" />\n\n<strong>2. Ban them permanently</strong>\n\nYour users do not have to be stuck with an annoying user anymore. Chatroom owners and moderators can now ban a member from a chatroom. Ban and unban your chatroom members anytime you like.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/ban_and_unban.png" alt="" />\n\n<strong>3. Chat History</strong>\n\nYou aren''t new to this plugin but what’s interesting is that chat history has now found its way into our chatrooms too. Retrieve your chatroom conversations and recall them whenever!\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/chat_history.png" alt="" />\n\n<strong>Games, now more competitive!</strong>\n\nPacked with an entirely new set of exciting and addictive games, this plugin makes sure your users never get bored again. What’s new? Leaderboard on the games module tracks your score and games. Don’t worry, next time you get a high score, leaderboard will record it for you. \n\nOur new games plugin has over 10,000+ games and our competitive leaderboard feature will ensure your users are glued to your site.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/games_updated2.png" alt="" />\n\n<strong>Your popups, your way!</strong>\n\nPlugins like writeboard, whiteboard, screen sharing and smilies can be given a new look in seconds. Re-size these popups so that they look good with your site. Yes it''s that simple!\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/11/resize.png" alt="" />\n\n<strong>Miscellaneous enhancements and bug fixes</strong>\n\nWe have added support for LinkedIn, transliterate plugin fix for chatrooms and improved join-room and smilies plugin. 100s of bugs have been fixed in this version to ensure to a smoother seamless process. Improved delivery performance of numeric and alpha numeric characters over one-on-one chats makes CometChat v4.6 the most appealing and fascinating version yet.\n\n<h2>Get CometChat v4.6!</h2>\n\nLoaded with brand new features and enhancements, CometChat v4.6 should definitely be on your wish list! \n\nWhat are you waiting for? <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/buy" title="Buy CometChat">Purchase CometChat today!</a> or <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/contact" title="Contact us">contact us</a> if you have any questions. \n\nAlready have CometChat? <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/my" title="Download CometChat">Download CometChat</a> or purchase our <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/my" title="Purchase Installation Service">installation service</a> if you would like us to perform the upgrade.\n', 'CometChat v4.6 - Where perfection begins', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '383-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '2013-09-25 11:22:43', '', 383, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/383-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(794, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '<a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/cometchattv" title="CometChatTV" target="_blank"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/06/cometchattv.jpg" alt="" title="cometchattv" width="640" height="150" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-284" /></a>\n\nWe have added new installation screencasts for CometChat at <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/cometchattv" title="CometChatTV" target="_blank"><strong>CometChatTV</strong></a>.\n\nSimply watch the installation video for your software and install CometChat within minutes on your site!\n\n\n\nView all our videos at our new <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/cometchattv" title="CometChatTV" target="_blank">Youtube Channel</a> or subscribe to stay informed.\n\n<a href="//www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user_id=Wu7LtG16A9ZgcyBpNMCX0Q&amp;feature=creators_cornier-//s.ytimg.com/yt/img/creators_corner/Subscribe_to_my_videos/YT_Subscribe_160x27_red.png"><img src="//s.ytimg.com/yt/img/creators_corner/Subscribe_to_my_videos/YT_Subscribe_160x27_red.png" style="border:0px" alt="Subscribe to me on YouTube" /></a>', 'CometChat Video Installation Guides!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '362-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '', 362, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/362-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(795, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '<h2>Screen sharing plugin now works with Adobe FMS</h2>\n\nWe have updated our screensharing plugin so you can use Adobe FMS server instead of RED5 server. Earlier you could use only RED5 which required some skills (or an external developer) to install. Now, if you do not wish to take the effort to self-host a RED5 server, you can simply subscribe at <a href="http://www.influxis.com" target="_blank">Influxis</a> for an Adobe FMS server.\n\nWith this release, all our plugins (screensharing, whiteboard and audio/video chat) can be configured to use either RED5 or Adobe FMS. Detailed installation instructions are available in our <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/documentation">documentation</a>. \n\nNote that audio/video chat, by default, uses our own servers and does not require any additional server. But we provide this option for customers who wish to use their own servers.\n\n<h2>Theme Helper</h2>\n\nWe have received a lot of requests for assistance with the theme variables. To make it easier to modify the look and feel of CometChat, we have created a simple theme helper which tells you which variable modifies which part of the theme.\n\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/theme-helper" target="_blank"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/08/themehelper.png" alt="" title="CometChat Theme Helper" width="472" height="499" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-353" /></a>\n\nCheck out our <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/theme-helper" title="CometChat Theme Variables Helper" target="_blank">theme helper</a> today and create your own custom theme with ease!\n\n<h2>End-user manuals</h2>\n\nYour end users may need guidance on how to use CometChat. With so many features, it may be difficult for some users to understand all the functionality. We have added PDFs which you can download for free and provide to your site users. \n\nSelect your edition and download the <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/end-user-manual" title="CometChat End User Manual">end-user manual</a> for your users now!\n\n<h2>Answers - Quicker troubleshooting!</h2>\n\nWe have added a new section which helps quickly answer your most common queries before you create a support ticket or look around in our community forums.\n\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/answers"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/08/answers.jpg" alt="" title="Answers" width="472" height="499" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-357" /></a>\n\nHead over to <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/answers">Answers</a> for all your CometChat troubleshooting/customization needs.', 'Screen sharing plugin, theme helper and end-user manuals', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '328-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '', 328, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/328-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(796, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', 'As you may be aware, our existing whiteboard and screen sharing plugins, made use Adobe LCCS. Adobe has decided to discontinue this service without prior intimation. When we first heard about this from Adobe, we immediately began work to create new plugins which <strong>do not</strong> rely on this service. \n\nAlong the way, we had a chance to add new features as well!\n\n<h2>Screen sharing with screen control</h2>\n\nThe new screen sharing plugin allows your users to control the screen remotely! Not only can your users view each other''s screens, they can also control them.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/06/ScreenshareFrontend3.png" alt="" title="Screen sharing" width="405" height="103" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-315" />\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/06/screenshareFrontend6.png" alt="" title="Screen viewing with control" width="642" height="509" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-317" />\n\n<h2>Whiteboard</h2>\n\nThe new whiteboard plugin has tons of new options and a cleaner layout which blends smoothly into our existing look and feel. \n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/06/whiteboardfront-end3.png" alt="" title="Whiteboard" width="643" height="514" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-319" />\n\n<h2>Requirements</h2>\n\nIf you would like to use the screen sharing, you will need RED5 server (open-source). The software can either be hosted on your own server or you can use a third-party host. You can learn more by reading up our <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/admin/plugins/screensharing-plugin">configuration guide for screen sharing</a>.\n\nIf you would like to use whiteboard plugin, you will need either RED5 (open-source) or Adobe FMS server (commercial). Both software can either be hosted on your own server or you can use a third-party host. You can learn more by reading up our <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/admin/plugins/whiteboard-plugin">configuration guide for whiteboard</a>.\n\nFeel free to <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/contact">email us</a> if you have any questions.', 'New Whiteboard and Screen sharing with screen control!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '311-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '', 311, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/311-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(797, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '<h2>CometChat for mooSocial</h2>\n\nmooSocial is an open source social network script built on top of CakePHP 2 framework. It has all the features to build a successful community (e.g. blog, photo, group, event, video, topic...). mooSocial is fast, easy to customize and CMS independent.\n\nCometChat seamlessly integrates with mooSocial! \n\n- Your users will be automatically logged in to CometChat when they login to your mooSocial site.\n- CometChat will automatically show friends in the Who''s Online list.\n- CometChat will integrate with your users'' avatar and profile links as well.\n\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/moosocial-chat"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/06/moosocial.jpg" alt="" title="CometChat for mooSocial" width="600" height="480" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-298" /></a>\n\nLearn more about the new <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/moosocial-chat">mooSocial chat</a>!\n\n<h2>CometChat for Oxwall</h2>\n\nOxwall is unbelievably flexible and easy to use open-source PHP/MySQL social networking software platform. Oxwall is used for a wide range of projects starting from family sites and custom social networks to collaboration tools and enterprise community solutions.\n\nCometChat seamlessly integrates with Oxwall! \n\n- Your users will be automatically logged in to CometChat when they login to your Oxwall site.\n- CometChat will automatically show friends in the Who''s Online list.\n- CometChat will integrate with your users'' avatar and profile links as well.\n\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/oxwall-chat"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/06/oxwall.jpg" alt="" title="CometChat for Oxwall" width="600" height="480" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-298" /></a>\n\nLearn more about the new <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/oxwall-chat">Oxwall chat</a>!\n\n<h2>Get CometChat!</h2>\n\nSo what are you waiting for? <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/buy" title="Buy CometChat">Purchase CometChat today!</a> or <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/contact" title="Contact us">contact us</a> if you have any questions.', 'New mooSocial and Oxwall seamless integrations for CometChat!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '297-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '2013-09-25 11:22:44', '', 297, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/297-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(798, 1, '2013-09-25 11:22:45', '2013-09-25 11:22:45', '<a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/cometchattv" title="CometChatTV" target="_blank"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2012/06/cometchattv.jpg" alt="" title="cometchattv" width="640" height="150" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-284" /></a>\n\nWe are happy to announce the launch of our new Youtube channel - <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/cometchattv" title="CometChatTV" target="_blank"><strong>CometChatTV</strong></a>!\n\nHaving a tough time understanding CometChat? Don''t get confused; CometChat enables your site users to chat with each other and their social networking friends in real-time. <strong>Check out our new introduction video.</strong>\n\n\n\nNeed to understand a particular feature? Now learn how to use CometChat with our new video tutorials. Our desktop messenger tutorial is guaranteed to get you excited!\n\n\n\nView all our videos at our new <a href="http://www.youtube.com/user/cometchattv" title="CometChatTV" target="_blank">Youtube Channel</a> or subscribe to stay informed of all our latest videos.\n\n<a href="//www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user_id=Wu7LtG16A9ZgcyBpNMCX0Q&amp;feature=creators_cornier-//s.ytimg.com/yt/img/creators_corner/Subscribe_to_my_videos/YT_Subscribe_160x27_red.png"><img src="//s.ytimg.com/yt/img/creators_corner/Subscribe_to_my_videos/YT_Subscribe_160x27_red.png" style="border:0px" alt="Subscribe to me on YouTube" /></a>', 'New video tutorials and tour!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '270-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 11:22:45', '2013-09-25 11:22:45', '', 270, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/blog/2013/09/25/270-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
