(1215, 1, '2012-08-23 14:22:53', '2012-08-23 08:52:53', 'To auto-enter into the chatroom, follow the steps listed below:\n\nLogin to <strong>CometChat Administration Panel</strong> -&gt; click on <strong>modules</strong> tab -&gt; <strong>"Configure Module"</strong> button next to Chatrooms.\n\nAdd chatroom ID in which you need to enter directly for <strong>"Auto enter chatroom ID"</strong> setting option. Then click on <strong>Update Settings</strong>.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/answers/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2012/05/auto_chatroom.jpg" alt="auto_chatroom" />\n\n', 'I need to directly enter into chatroom. Is this possible?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'i-need-to-directly-enter-into-chatroom-is-this-possible', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:22:53', '2012-08-23 08:52:53', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1215', 0, 'post', '', 0),
