(682, 600, 'extra1', '<p>Edit cometchat/integration.php and find:</p>\r\n<pre><code>define(''DB_USERNAME'',''USERNAME'');\r\ndefine(''DB_PASSWORD'',''PASSWORD'');\r\ndefine(''DB_NAME'',''DATABASE'');\r\n</pre></code>\r\n\r\n<p>And replace it with your actual database values (can be found in <em>config/site.php</em>), e.g.</p>\r\n<pre><code>define(''DB_USERNAME'',''concrete_user'');\r\ndefine(''DB_PASSWORD'',''toughpassword'');\r\ndefine(''DB_NAME'',''concrete5'');\r\n</pre></code>\r\n<p>Save your cometchat/integration.php file.</p>'),
(683, 600, 'kalinsPDFMeta', '{"showLink":"default"}'),
(684, 600, '_wp_page_template', 'install-page.php'),
(685, 608, '_edit_last', '1');
