(1344, 1, '2012-05-18 14:55:53', '2012-05-18 09:25:53', 'This feature allows you to communicate with your visitors in real time.  \n\nYou can enter your *announcements* in the *Announcement Text Area* provided and your visitors will get them immediately.\n\nSet the *Show Only to logged-in Users?* to *Yes*, to enable only your *logged in* users to view the announcement.\n\n![New Announcements1]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/New+announcement1.png)\n\nTo remove an old announcement, click on the ![Remove](http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/remove.png) button.\n\n![Remove Announcements]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/Remove+announcements.png)\n', 'Announcements', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'announcements', '', '', '2012-05-18 14:55:53', '2012-05-18 09:25:53', '', 54, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1344', 32, 'page', '', 0),
