(1360, 1, '2012-05-18 15:07:54', '2012-05-18 09:37:54', 'You have the option to set CometChat to show all the online users or all the friends in the *"Who''s Online" List.*\n\n![Who''s Online List]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/whos-online-list.png)\n\n&gt; Displaying all online users is recommended for small sites only\n\n&gt; If your CometChat Admin Panel does not have this section, then your site does not have a friends feature so CometChat will automatically show all online users.', 'Who''s Online List', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'whos-online-list', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:07:54', '2012-05-18 09:37:54', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1360', 18, 'page', '', 0),
(1362, 1, '2012-04-30 16:14:10', '2012-04-30 10:44:10', '', 'Who''s Online List', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'whos-online-list', '', '', '2012-04-30 16:14:10', '2012-04-30 10:44:10', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/whos-online-list.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1383, 1, '2012-05-18 15:09:17', '2012-05-18 09:39:17', 'CometService offloads 95% of work to our servers and reduces message delivery time.	\r\n\r\nCometService can be activated directly from the CometChat Administration Panel. \r\n\r\nTo use CometService, you need to perform two easy steps.\r\n\r\n<h4>Obtaining Keys</h4>\r\n\r\n1. Point your browser to [http://www.cometchat.com/cometservice](http://www.cometchat.com/cometservice) and select a plan of your choice\r\n2. After subscribing, you will receive an automated email from us\r\n3. Login to CometChat.com and visit [http://www.cometchat.com/my/cometservice](http://www.cometchat.com/my/cometservice)\r\n4. Copy the keys from the page \r\n\r\n<h4>Adding the Keys</h4>\r\n1. Login to *CometChat Administration Panel*\r\n2. Select *Settings -&gt; CometService*\r\n3. Enter the keys and set *Use CometService* to *Yes*\r\n\r\n![Comet Service]\r\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/CometService.png)\r\n\r\n', 'CometService', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'comet-service', '', '', '2013-09-23 12:51:11', '2013-09-23 12:51:11', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1383', 19, 'page', '', 0),
(1395, 1, '2012-04-30 17:05:23', '2012-04-30 11:35:23', '', 'Comet Service', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'cometservice-2', '', '', '2012-04-30 17:05:23', '2012-04-30 11:35:23', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/CometService.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1409, 1, '2012-05-18 15:10:14', '2012-05-18 09:40:14', 'With this feature, you can enable your visitors to automatically log into CometChat when they visit your site as Guests12432 etc.\r\n\r\nYou can configure which set of users will be displayed in the Who’s Online List for logged in users as well as for visitors.		\r\n\r\n<h4>Guest Chat Configuration</h4>		\r\n1. Login to *CometChat Administration Panel*	\r\n\r\n2. Select *Settings -&gt; Guest Chat*	\r\n\r\n3. Enable *Guest Chat*	\r\n\r\n4. Set the *Prefix for guest names, Who’s Online List for guests* and *logged in users* accordingly.	\r\n\r\n5. Click on the *Update* button		\r\n\r\n![Guest Chat](http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/03/guestchat.png)', 'Guest Chat', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'guest-chat', '', '', '2013-09-23 12:51:27', '2013-09-23 12:51:27', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1409', 20, 'page', '', 0),
(1417, 1, '2012-04-30 17:28:16', '2012-04-30 11:58:16', '', 'Guest Chat', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'guest-chat', '', '', '2012-04-30 17:28:16', '2012-04-30 11:58:16', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/Guest-Chat.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1434, 1, '2012-05-18 15:11:12', '2012-05-18 09:41:12', 'With this feature you can ban a particular user or add words to the list of abusive words.			\n\n![banned words](http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/03/bannedwords.png)	\n\nTo know the ID of a user, click on the Don’t know ID link and enter the username in the new window that opens and then click on the *Search Database* button.		\n\n![Find User ID](http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/Find+User+ID+1.png)	\n\nBanned users will not be able to use IM and chatroom functionality of CometChat	\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Please use comma to separate IDs and words</p>\n</blockquote>', 'Banned words and users', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'banned-words-and-users', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:11:12', '2012-05-18 09:41:12', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1434', 21, 'page', '', 0),
(1436, 1, '2012-04-30 18:04:07', '2012-04-30 12:34:07', '', 'Banned words and users', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'banned-words-and-users', '', '', '2012-04-30 18:04:07', '2012-04-30 12:34:07', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/Banned-words-and-users.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
