(1521, 1, '2012-05-18 15:12:32', '2012-05-18 09:42:32', 'If the Base URL is incorrect, CometChat will stop working on your site.\n\n#Update Base URL\nIf you are using CometChat over a cross domain or sub domain then the *Base URL detection algorithm* may fail to detect your site''s *base URL*. Therefore in this case you will have to put the **Base URL manually**.\n\nFor example, if *www.yoursite.com* is your **main domain** and **CometChat** is **installed at alternate domain** i.e. *www.chat.yoursite1.com*, in this case your base URL will be *http://www.chat.yoursite1.com* \n\n![Update Base URL new]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/05/Update+base+URL+new.png)\n\nIn most cases, your *Base URL* will be */cometchat/*', 'Change Base URL', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'change-base-url', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:12:32', '2012-05-18 09:42:32', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1521', 22, 'page', '', 0),
