(1543, 1, '2012-05-18 15:13:37', '2012-05-18 09:43:37', 'This feature allows you to *disable* CometChat temporarily on your site.\n\nTo disable CometChat, set the option to *Yes* and then click on the *Update* button.\n\n![Disable CometChat]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/Disable+CometChat.png)', 'Disable CometChat', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'disable-cometchat', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:13:37', '2012-05-18 09:43:37', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1543', 25, 'page', '', 0),
