(1558, 1, '2012-05-18 15:13:15', '2012-05-18 09:43:15', 'To change your username and password go to  *CometChat Administration Panel -&gt; Settings  -&gt; Change Admin User / Pass.*\n		\nEnter your new username and password, then click on the *Change User/Pass* button.\n\n![Change administration username and password](http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/04/Change+administration+username+and+password.png)\n\n*Note:* Do not use ''or  in your username or password.\n', 'Change Admin User/Pass', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'change-admin-userpass', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:13:15', '2012-05-18 09:43:15', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1558', 23, 'page', '', 0),
