(1569, 1, '2012-05-18 15:03:47', '2012-05-18 09:33:47', 'You can add *custom advertisements* to chat boxes and earn money when your users chat. Advertisements will be automatically displayed in the active chat box.\r\nYou can use any *custom HTML code* as per your requirements.	\r\n\r\n<h4>Configuring the Module</h4>\r\n\r\n1. In the *Extensions* section, add the *Advertisement extension* to your live extensions and click on the *Configure Module* icon besides the name.	\r\n\r\n2. Enter your *Advertisement HTML code* and set the *Ad height*.	\r\n\r\n3. Click on the *Update Settings* button and close the window.		\r\n\r\n![Advertisement Settings](http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/05/Advertisement+Settings.png)', 'Advertisements', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'advertisements', '', '', '2013-09-23 12:47:54', '2013-09-23 12:47:54', '', 630, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1569', 15, 'page', '', 0),
