(1657, 1, '2012-05-18 15:21:39', '2012-05-18 09:51:39', 'If you have a downloaded a theme for CometChat and want to upload it, you can use our installation facility to add the new theme to your site.	\n\nTo upload the new theme, first *browse* the theme and then click on the *Add Theme* button.\n\n![Upload new theme]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/05/Upload+new+theme.png)', 'Upload theme', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'upload-theme', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:21:39', '2012-05-18 09:51:39', '', 195, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1657', 14, 'page', '', 0),
