(2264, 1, '2012-05-18 14:48:21', '2012-05-18 09:18:21', 'After you login, you will be taken to the dashboard which will show you statistics of CometChat on your site.	\n\n![dashboard](http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/03/dasboard.png "dashboard")		\n\nYou can also give us your testimonial by clicking on the write us a testimonial link. Fill in the required information along with your testimonial and click on the Submit button.		\n		\n![Testimonial](http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/03/testimonial.png "testimonial")', 'Dashboard', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'dashboard', '', '', '2012-05-18 14:48:21', '2012-05-18 09:18:21', '', 54, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=2264', 29, 'page', '', 0),
