(2301, 1, '2012-05-18 14:53:03', '2012-05-18 09:23:03', 'You can monitor conversations taking place on your site in real-time.\n\nTo monitor these conversation go to *CometChat Admin Panel -&gt; monitor*\n\n![Monitor Conversations]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/05/monitor1.png)\n\n&gt; This feature can be disabled on request. Please create a support ticket if you would like to do so.', 'Monitor', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'monitor', '', '', '2012-05-18 14:53:03', '2012-05-18 09:23:03', '', 54, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=2301', 38, 'page', '', 0),
