(3964, 1, '2012-11-12 17:06:30', '2012-11-12 11:36:30', 'Add the copied code in your <strong>index_top.tpl</strong> file immediately after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag. This file is generally present at <strong>/templates//index_top.tpl</strong>', 'PG Dating Pro', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'pgdatingpro', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:33:37', '2013-09-24 07:33:37', '', 146, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=3964', 111, 'page', '', 0),
