(3976, 1, '2012-12-20 18:18:43', '2012-12-20 12:48:43', '1) You need to download the latest version of <a href="http://coding.bezslabostei.ru/FooterManager/Download" target="_blank">Footer Manager Extension</a> and extract it into the\r\nextensions folder of your MediaWiki installation.\r\n\r\n2) Enable the extension by adding this line to your LocalSettings.php file:\r\n\r\n`require_once (''extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php'');`\r\n\r\n3) For CometChat to appear on your site, you need to make following changes in the <strong>extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php</strong> file.\r\ni) Assign the footer code to the key ‘headscript’.\r\nii) Assign the value of key ‘icon’ and ‘bottomscript’ to null.\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n`$wgFooterManagerBanners[] = array(\r\n''headscript'' =&gt; '''',\r\n''icon'' =&gt; '''',\r\n''bottomscript'' =&gt;'''',\r\n);`', 'MediaWiki', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'mediawiki', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:26:47', '2013-09-24 07:26:47', '', 146, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=3976', 100, 'page', '', 0),
(3981, 1, '2012-12-20 18:20:15', '2012-12-20 12:50:15', 'Your header file should be <strong>/templates/header.tpl</strong>. Edit the file using any text editor.\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	\r\n	', 'Woltlab', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'woltlab', '', '', '2013-09-24 08:01:41', '2013-09-24 08:01:41', '', 146, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=3981', 137, 'page', '', 0),
