(4225, 1, '2013-03-14 16:24:32', '2013-03-14 10:54:32', '* Point your browser to the following URL: <strong>https://developer.addlive.com/cometchat</strong> or click on the link in the plugin setting window to create an AddLive account if you don’t have an Application ID and an Application Auth Secret key	\r\n\r\n* Register on the site with the required details		\r\n\r\n* Once you are done with the registration process, you will receive a mail from AddLive containing the Application ID and Stable API key	\r\n\r\n* Now place these values in plugin setting window and click on the <strong>Update</strong> settings	\r\n\r\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/03/addlive_full-300x295.png" alt="addlive_full"  class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4231" />', 'AddLive', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'addlive', '', '', '2013-09-25 04:22:03', '2013-09-25 04:22:03', '', 2881, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=4225', 0, 'page', '', 0),
