k which maybe adequate for small/medium sites. Google charges $20 for 1 million characters and is not a monthly subscription. Learn more about <a href="http://go.microsoft.com/?linkid=9782667">Microsoft''s pricing</a> and <a href="http://code.google.com/apis/language/translate/v2/pricing.html">Google''s pricing</a>.\r\n\r\n<h4>  Facebook/Gtalk Chat Extension</h4> \r\n\r\nAs this is a hosted solution, it is a free benefit we provide to all **active** CometChat license holders. If your license has expired, you can renew it for 50% of the edition price.', 'System Requirements', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '142-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:23:51', '2013-09-24 06:23:51', '', 142, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/142-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
