 Microsoft provides a free subscription pack which maybe adequate for small/medium sites. Google charges $20 for 1 million characters and is not a monthly subscription. Learn more about <a href="http://go.microsoft.com/?linkid=9782667" target="_blank">Microsoft''s pricing</a> and <a href="http://code.google.com/apis/language/translate/v2/pricing.html" target="_blank">Google''s pricing</a>.\r\n\r\n<h4>  Facebook/Gtalk Chat Extension</h4> \r\n\r\nAs this is a hosted solution, it is a free benefit we provide to all <strong>active</strong> CometChat license holders. If your license has expired, you can renew it for 50% of the edition price.', 'System Requirements', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '142-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:29:58', '2013-09-24 06:29:58', '', 142, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/142-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4773, 1, '2013-09-24 06:33:24', '2013-09-24 06:33:24', 'CometChat can be downloaded directly from our website. Simply click on <strong><em>My Purchases</em></strong> link and download the latest version.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4699" alt="downloading-cometchat" src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat-300x192.png" width="300" height="192" /></a>\r\n\r\nIf you plan to install CometChat on a test domain initially, make sure you enter the same domain before download. You can change the domain later, when you move to your production site.\r\n\r\nIf you are planning to use CometChat for a custom coded site, then select the <strong><em>Standalone Site</em></strong> integration from the drop-down menu.\r\n\r\n<blockquote>By default, the latest version of CometChat is already selected. We recommend you download the latest unless you have a strong reason not to do so.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat.png"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat-300x192.png" alt="downloading-cometchat" width="300" height="192" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4699" /></a>', 'Downloading CometChat', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '168-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:33:24', '2013-09-24 06:33:24', '', 168, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/168-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4774, 1, '2013-09-24 06:35:59', '2013-09-24 06:35:59', 'CometChat can be downloaded directly from our website. Simply click on <strong><em>My Purchases</em></strong> link and download the latest version.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4699" alt="downloading-cometchat" src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat-300x192.png" width="300" height="192" />\r\n\r\nIf you plan to install CometChat on a test domain initially, make sure you enter the same domain before download. You can change the domain later, when you move to your production site.\r\n\r\nIf you are planning to use CometChat for a custom coded site, then select the <strong><em>Standalone Site</em></strong>  integration from the drop-down menu.\r\n\r\n<blockquote>By default, the latest version of CometChat is already selected. We recommend you download the latest unless you have a strong reason not to do so.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat-300x192.png" alt="downloading-cometchat" width="300" height="192" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4699" />', 'Downloading CometChat', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '168-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:35:59', '2013-09-24 06:35:59', '', 168, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/168-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4775, 1, '2013-09-24 06:40:55', '2013-09-24 06:40:55', 'CometChat can be downloaded directly from our website. Simply click on <em>My Purchases</em> link and download the latest version.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4699" alt="downloading-cometchat" src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat-300x192.png" width="300" height="192" />\r\n\r\nIf you plan to install CometChat on a test domain initially, make sure you enter the same domain before download. You can change the domain later, when you move to your production site.\r\n\r\nIf you are planning to use CometChat for a custom coded site, then select the <em>Standalone Site</em>  integration from the drop-down menu.\r\n\r\n<blockquote>By default, the latest version of CometChat is already selected. We recommend you download the latest unless you have a strong reason not to do so.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat-300x192.png" alt="downloading-cometchat" width="300" height="192" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4699" />', 'Downloading CometChat', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '168-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:40:55', '2013-09-24 06:40:55', '', 168, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/168-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4776, 1, '2013-09-24 06:41:43', '2013-09-24 06:41:43', 'CometChat can be downloaded directly from our website. Simply click on <strong>My Purchases</strong> link and download the latest version.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4699" alt="downloading-cometchat" src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat-300x192.png" width="300" height="192" />\r\n\r\nIf you plan to install CometChat on a test domain initially, make sure you enter the same domain before download. You can change the domain later, when you move to your production site.\r\n\r\nIf you are planning to use CometChat for a custom coded site, then select the <strong>Standalone Site</strong>  integration from the drop-down menu.\r\n\r\n<blockquote>By default, the latest version of CometChat is already selected. We recommend you download the latest unless you have a strong reason not to do so.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/09/downloading_cometchat-300x192.png" alt="downloading-cometchat" width="300" height="192" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4699" />', 'Downloading CometChat', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '168-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:41:43', '2013-09-24 06:41:43', '', 168, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/168-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4777, 1, '2013-09-24 06:45:41', '2013-09-24 06:45:41', 'CometChat can be installed and integrated with virtually any website. If you are integrating CometChat with a software which has a ready integration available, then it should take you about 5 minutes to install CometChat.\n\nIf you are integrating CometChat with a custom site and have programming knowledge, refer to the <a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/installing-cometchat/custom-coded-site">Custom Coded Site</a> guides. CometChat can be integrated with any PHP, .NET, Classic ASP, Ruby on Rails etc. website. Please make sure that your server must meet the minimum requirements.\n\nIf you are integrating CometChat with a custom site but do not have programming knowledge, simply <a href="/buy"></a>[purchase](http://www.cometchat.com/buy) our Premium or Platinum Edition and our trained professionals will perform the complete installation and integration of CometChat on your site. We guarantee installation of CometChat on your site.', 'Installing CometChat', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4439-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:45:41', '2013-09-24 06:45:41', '', 4439, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/4439-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4778, 1, '2013-09-24 06:46:08', '2013-09-24 06:46:08', 'CometChat can be installed and integrated with virtually any website. If you are integrating CometChat with a software which has a ready integration available, then it should take you about 5 minutes to install CometChat.\r\n\r\nIf you are integrating CometChat with a custom site and have programming knowledge, refer to the <a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/installing-cometchat/custom-coded-site">Custom Coded Site</a> guides. CometChat can be integrated with any PHP, .NET, Classic ASP, Ruby on Rails etc. website. Please make sure that your server must meet the minimum requirements.\r\n\r\nIf you are integrating CometChat with a custom site but do not have programming knowledge, simply <a href="/buy">purchase</a> our Premium or Platinum Edition and our trained professionals will perform the complete installation and integration of CometChat on your site. We guarantee installation of CometChat on your site.', 'Installing CometChat', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4439-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:46:08', '2013-09-24 06:46:08', '', 4439, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/4439-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4779, 1, '2013-09-24 06:47:11', '2013-09-24 06:47:11', 'Installing CometChat with ready integration will only take you a few minutes. Please select a software from below. If your software does not feature below, please view the <strong>Custom Coded Site</strong> section.', 'Ready Integrations', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '146-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:47:11', '2013-09-24 06:47:11', '', 146, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/146-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4780, 1, '2013-09-24 06:49:57', '2013-09-24 06:49:57', 'Login to WordPress Administration and go to <strong>Appearances</strong> -> <strong>Editor</strong>. Click on <strong>Header (header.php)</strong> from the right side panel to edit the header.\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	', 'BuddyPress', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '327-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:49:57', '2013-09-24 06:49:57', '', 327, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/327-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4781, 1, '2013-09-24 06:51:31', '2013-09-24 06:51:31', 'Your template file should be <strong>/app/views/layouts/default.ctp</strong>\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	', 'CakePHP', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3973-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:51:31', '2013-09-24 06:51:31', '', 3973, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/3973-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4782, 1, '2013-09-24 06:54:03', '2013-09-24 06:54:03', 'Login to your <strong>Joomla Administration</strong> (usually http://www.domain.com/administrator)\r\n\r\nUnder the <strong>Extensions</strong> tab, select the <strong>Template Manager</strong> option.\r\n\r\nNow select the template which has a star next to it i.e. the template in which you want to add CometChat.\r\n\r\nClick on the <strong>Edit HTML</strong> button (top-right corner)\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>	\r\n	\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote>If you are unable to find `` tag, then please [add the code manually using this guide](http://www.cometchat.com/answers/i-am-unable-to-find-html-code-in-my-joomla-site-template/).</blockquote>\r\n\r\n ', 'Community Builder', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:54:03', '2013-09-24 06:54:03', '', 34, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/34-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `ccwp_4_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(4783, 1, '2013-09-24 06:56:04', '2013-09-24 06:56:04', 'Login to your <strong>Joomla Administration</strong> (usually http://www.domain.com/administrator)\n\nUnder the <strong>Extensions</strong> tab, select the <strong>Template Manager</strong> option.\n\nNow select the template which has a star next to it i.e. the template in which you want to add CometChat.\n\nClick on the <strong>Edit HTML</strong> button (top-right corner)\n\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\n\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\n</code></pre>	\n	\n\n\n<blockquote>If you are unable to find `<code>&lt;head&gt;</code>` tag, then please [add the code manually using this guide]().</blockquote>\n\n ', 'Community Builder', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '34-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:56:04', '2013-09-24 06:56:04', '', 34, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/34-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4784, 1, '2013-09-24 06:56:30', '2013-09-24 06:56:30', 'Login to your <strong>Joomla Administration</strong> (usually http://www.domain.com/administrator)\r\n\r\nUnder the <strong>Extensions</strong> tab, select the <strong>Template Manager</strong> option.\r\n\r\nNow select the template which has a star next to it i.e. the template in which you want to add CometChat.\r\n\r\nClick on the <strong>Edit HTML</strong> button (top-right corner)\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>	\r\n	\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote>If you are unable to find `<code>&lt;head&gt;</code>` tag, then please <a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/answers/i-am-unable-to-find-html-code-in-my-joomla-site-template/">add the code manually using this guide</a>.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n ', 'Community Builder', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:56:30', '2013-09-24 06:56:30', '', 34, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/34-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4785, 1, '2013-09-24 06:56:53', '2013-09-24 06:56:53', 'Login to your <strong>Joomla Administration</strong> (usually http://www.domain.com/administrator)\r\n\r\nUnder the <strong>Extensions</strong> tab, select the <strong>Template Manager</strong> option.\r\n\r\nNow select the template which has a star next to it i.e. the template in which you want to add CometChat.\r\n\r\nClick on the <strong>Edit HTML</strong> button (top-right corner)\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>	\r\n	\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote>If you are unable to find <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag, then please <a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/answers/i-am-unable-to-find-html-code-in-my-joomla-site-template/">add the code manually using this guide</a>.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n ', 'Community Builder', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '34-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:56:53', '2013-09-24 06:56:53', '', 34, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/34-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4786, 1, '2013-09-24 06:58:25', '2013-09-24 06:58:25', 'The header file for concrete5 is:\r\n\r\n<strong>/concrete5/concrete/elements/header_required.php</strong>\r\n\r\nImmediately add the copied code to the top of the file.', 'Concrete5', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '600-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 06:58:25', '2013-09-24 06:58:25', '', 600, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/600-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4787, 1, '2013-09-24 07:04:35', '2013-09-24 07:04:35', 'Add the copied code into your Drupal <strong>page.tpl.php</strong> file immediately after the `` tag. This file is generally present at <strong>/themes/garland/page.tpl.php</strong> (where <strong>garland</strong> is your theme)', 'Drupal', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '330-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:04:35', '2013-09-24 07:04:35', '', 330, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/330-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4788, 1, '2013-09-24 07:06:02', '2013-09-24 07:06:02', 'If you are using the <strong>handshakes_plain</strong> template, then the header file will be:\r\n\r\n<strong>/themes/handshakes_plain/templates/source/header.tpl</strong>\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	', 'Dzoic Handshakes', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '332-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:06:02', '2013-09-24 07:06:02', '', 332, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/332-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4789, 1, '2013-09-24 07:08:06', '2013-09-24 07:08:06', 'If you are using the <strong>default</strong> template, then the header file will be:\r\n\r\n<strong>e107_themes/templates/header_default.php</strong>\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	', 'e107', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '597-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:08:06', '2013-09-24 07:08:06', '', 597, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/597-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4790, 1, '2013-09-24 07:09:30', '2013-09-24 07:09:30', 'Insert the copied code into your Elgg <strong>header.php</strong> file immediately after the `` tag.\r\n\r\nThis file is generally present at <strong>/views/default/page/elements/head.php</strong>', 'Elgg', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '334-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:09:30', '2013-09-24 07:09:30', '', 334, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/334-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4791, 1, '2013-09-24 07:10:46', '2013-09-24 07:10:46', 'Login to your <strong>Administration Panel</strong>\r\n\r\nClick on <strong>Design</strong> -&gt; <strong>Templates</strong> -&gt; <strong>Global Variables</strong>\r\n\r\nClick on <strong>html_head</strong> and add the copied code at the end of <strong>Variable Content</strong>.', 'ExpressionEngine', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '539-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:10:46', '2013-09-24 07:10:46', '', 539, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/539-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4792, 1, '2013-09-24 07:11:54', '2013-09-24 07:11:54', 'Login to your IPB Admin Control Panel (usually http://www.domain.com/forums/admin)\r\n\r\nUnder the <strong>Look &amp; Feel</strong> tab, click on the skin name in which you want to add the bar. Now under <strong>Global Templates</strong>, select <strong>globalTemplate</strong>.\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	', 'Invision Power Board', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '336-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:11:54', '2013-09-24 07:11:54', '', 336, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/336-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4793, 1, '2013-09-24 07:12:39', '2013-09-24 07:12:39', 'Add the copied code in your <strong>jr_header.tpl</strong> file immediately after the `` tag. This file is generally present at <strong>/skins/Nova/jr_header.tpl</strong>', 'JamRoom', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '338-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:12:39', '2013-09-24 07:12:39', '', 338, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/338-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4794, 1, '2013-09-24 07:16:09', '2013-09-24 07:16:09', 'Edit the file <strong>themes/default/page.tpl.php</strong> and paste the copied code just after the *``* tag.', 'Jcow', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '608-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:16:09', '2013-09-24 07:16:09', '', 608, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/608-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4795, 1, '2013-09-24 07:16:29', '2013-09-24 07:16:29', 'Edit the file <strong>themes/default/page.tpl.php</strong> and paste the copied code just after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag.', 'Jcow', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '608-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:16:29', '2013-09-24 07:16:29', '', 608, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/608-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
