(4802, 1, '2013-09-24 07:23:55', '2013-09-24 07:23:55', 'Login to your Joomla Administration (usually http://www.domain.com/administrator)\n\nUnder the <strong>Extensions</strong> tab, select the <strong>Template Manager</strong> option.\n\nNow select the template which has a star next to it i.e. the template in which you want to add CometChat.\n\nClick on the <strong>Edit HTML</strong> button (top-right corner)\n\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\n</code></pre>\n	\n	\n\n\n<blockquote>If you are unable to find <code>&lt;head&gt;\n</code> tag, then please <a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/troubleshooting/unable-to-find-html-code-in-joomla-template"></a>[add the code manually using this guide].</blockquote>\n', 'Kunena', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '346-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:23:55', '2013-09-24 07:23:55', '', 346, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/346-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4803, 1, '2013-09-24 07:24:05', '2013-09-24 07:24:05', 'Login to your Joomla Administration (usually http://www.domain.com/administrator)\r\n\r\nUnder the <strong>Extensions</strong> tab, select the <strong>Template Manager</strong> option.\r\n\r\nNow select the template which has a star next to it i.e. the template in which you want to add CometChat.\r\n\r\nClick on the <strong>Edit HTML</strong> button (top-right corner)\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n	\r\n	\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote>If you are unable to find <code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code> tag, then please <a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/troubleshooting/unable-to-find-html-code-in-joomla-template">add the code manually using this guide</a>.</blockquote>', 'Kunena', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '346-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:24:05', '2013-09-24 07:24:05', '', 346, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/346-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4804, 1, '2013-09-24 07:24:44', '2013-09-24 07:24:44', '1) You need to download the latest version of [Footer Manager Extension](http://coding.bezslabostei.ru/FooterManager/Download) and extract it into the\r\nextensions folder of your MediaWiki installation.\r\n\r\n2) Enable the extension by adding this line to your LocalSettings.php file:\r\n\r\n`require_once (''extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php'');`\r\n\r\n3) For CometChat to appear on your site, you need to make following changes in the <strong>extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php</strong> file.\r\ni) Assign the footer code to the key ‘headscript’.\r\nii) Assign the value of key ‘icon’ and ‘bottomscript’ to null.\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n`$wgFooterManagerBanners[] = array(\r\n''headscript'' =&gt; '''',\r\n''icon'' =&gt; '''',\r\n''bottomscript'' =&gt;'''',\r\n);`', 'MediaWiki', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3976-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:24:44', '2013-09-24 07:24:44', '', 3976, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/3976-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4805, 1, '2013-09-24 07:26:45', '2013-09-24 07:26:45', '1) You need to download the latest version of <a href="http://coding.bezslabostei.ru/FooterManager/Download" target="_blank">Footer Manager Extension</a> and extract it into the\nextensions folder of your MediaWiki installation.\n\n2) Enable the extension by adding this line to your LocalSettings.php file:\n\n`require_once (''extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php'');`\n\n3) For CometChat to appear on your site, you need to make following changes in the <strong>extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php</strong> file.\ni) Assign the footer code to the key ‘headscript’.\nii) Assign the value of key ‘icon’ and ‘bottomscript’ to null.\n\nFor example:\n\n`$wgFooterManagerBanners[] = array(\n''headscript'' =&gt; '''',\n''icon'' =&gt; '''',\n''bottomscript'' =&gt;'''',\n);`', 'MediaWiki', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3976-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:26:45', '2013-09-24 07:26:45', '', 3976, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/3976-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4806, 1, '2013-09-24 07:26:47', '2013-09-24 07:26:47', '1) You need to download the latest version of <a href="http://coding.bezslabostei.ru/FooterManager/Download" target="_blank">Footer Manager Extension</a> and extract it into the\r\nextensions folder of your MediaWiki installation.\r\n\r\n2) Enable the extension by adding this line to your LocalSettings.php file:\r\n\r\n`require_once (''extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php'');`\r\n\r\n3) For CometChat to appear on your site, you need to make following changes in the <strong>extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php</strong> file.\r\ni) Assign the footer code to the key ‘headscript’.\r\nii) Assign the value of key ‘icon’ and ‘bottomscript’ to null.\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n`$wgFooterManagerBanners[] = array(\r\n''headscript'' =&gt; '''',\r\n''icon'' =&gt; '''',\r\n''bottomscript'' =&gt;'''',\r\n);`', 'MediaWiki', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3976-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:26:47', '2013-09-24 07:26:47', '', 3976, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/3976-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4807, 1, '2013-09-24 07:27:40', '2013-09-24 07:27:40', 'Add the copied code in your  <strong>default.ctp</strong> file immediately after the  tag. This file is generally present at <strong>/app/View/Themed/THEMENAME/Layouts/default.ctp</strong>', 'mooSocial', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2864-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:27:40', '2013-09-24 07:27:40', '', 2864, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/2864-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4808, 1, '2013-09-24 07:28:26', '2013-09-24 07:28:26', 'Login to your myBB Administration (usually http://www.domain.com/mybb/admin)\r\n\r\nSelect <strong>Templates &amp; Styles</strong> option and then <strong>Templates</strong>.\r\n\r\nNow select the template you would like to add CometChat in (e.g. Default template) and then choose the index file.\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	', 'myBB', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '348-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:28:26', '2013-09-24 07:28:26', '', 348, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/348-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4809, 1, '2013-09-24 07:29:54', '2013-09-24 07:29:54', 'Login to your Joomla Administration (usually http://www.domain.com/administrator)\n\nUnder the <strong>Extensions</strong> tab, select the <strong>Template Manager</strong> option.\n\nNow select the template which has a star next to it i.e. the template in which you want to add CometChat.\n\nClick on the <strong>Edit HTML</strong> button (top-right corner)\n\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n	\n	\n\n\n<blockquote>If you are unable to find <code>&lt;head&gt;\n</code> tag, then please <a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/answers/i-am-unable-to-find-html-code-in-my-joomla-site-template/">add the code manually using this guide</a>.</blockquote>', 'Offiria', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3957-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:29:54', '2013-09-24 07:29:54', '', 3957, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/3957-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4810, 1, '2013-09-24 07:29:56', '2013-09-24 07:29:56', 'Login to your Joomla Administration (usually http://www.domain.com/administrator)\r\n\r\nUnder the <strong>Extensions</strong> tab, select the <strong>Template Manager</strong> option.\r\n\r\nNow select the template which has a star next to it i.e. the template in which you want to add CometChat.\r\n\r\nClick on the <strong>Edit HTML</strong> button (top-right corner)\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	\r\n	\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote>If you are unable to find <code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code> tag, then please <a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/answers/i-am-unable-to-find-html-code-in-my-joomla-site-template/">add the code manually using this guide</a>.</blockquote>', 'Offiria', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3957-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:29:56', '2013-09-24 07:29:56', '', 3957, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/3957-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4811, 1, '2013-09-24 07:31:35', '2013-09-24 07:31:35', 'Add the copied code in your <strong>index_header.tpl</strong> file immediately after the <code> tag. This file is generally present at <strong>/templates/default/index_header.tpl</strong>', 'osDate', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '350-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:31:35', '2013-09-24 07:31:35', '', 350, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/350-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4812, 1, '2013-09-24 07:31:46', '2013-09-24 07:31:46', 'Add the copied code in your <strong>index_header.tpl</strong> file immediately after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag. This file is generally present at <strong>/templates/default/index_header.tpl</strong>', 'osDate', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '350-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:31:46', '2013-09-24 07:31:46', '', 350, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/350-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4813, 1, '2013-09-24 07:33:37', '2013-09-24 07:33:37', 'Add the copied code in your <strong>index_top.tpl</strong> file immediately after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag. This file is generally present at <strong>/templates//index_top.tpl</strong>', 'PG Dating Pro', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3964-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:33:37', '2013-09-24 07:33:37', '', 3964, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/3964-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4814, 1, '2013-09-24 07:34:33', '2013-09-24 07:34:33', 'Add the copied code in your <strong>index_top.tpl</strong> file immediately after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag. This file is generally present at <strong>/templates/&lt;theme_name&gt;/index_top.tpl</strong>', 'PG SocialBiz', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3959-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:34:33', '2013-09-24 07:34:33', '', 3959, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/3959-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4815, 1, '2013-09-24 07:35:14', '2013-09-24 07:35:14', 'Login to your phpBB Administration Control Panel\r\n\r\nUnder the <strong>Styles</strong> tab, select the <strong>Templates</strong> option.\r\n\r\nNow click on the Edit link next to the template in which you want to add CometChat.\r\n\r\nSelect <strong>overall_header.html</strong> from the dropdown menu.\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	', 'phpBB', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '27-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:35:14', '2013-09-24 07:35:14', '', 27, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/27-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4816, 1, '2013-09-24 07:36:06', '2013-09-24 07:36:06', 'If you are using the <strong>default</strong> template, then the header file will be:\r\n\r\n<strong>/theme/frontend/default/template/template.html.php</strong>\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	', 'phpFox', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '353-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:36:06', '2013-09-24 07:36:06', '', 353, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/353-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4817, 1, '2013-09-24 07:36:40', '2013-09-24 07:36:40', 'Add the copied code in your theme''s <strong>header.php</strong> file immediately after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag.\r\n\r\nThis file is generally present at <strong>/themes/THEMENAME/html/header.php</strong>', 'Sharetronix', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '355-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:36:40', '2013-09-24 07:36:40', '', 355, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/355-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4818, 1, '2013-09-24 07:37:51', '2013-09-24 07:37:51', 'Now add the two copied lines to your site header by editing the following file in your SMF installation directory:\r\n\r\nFor SMF v1 - \r\n<strong>index.php</strong>\r\n\r\nFor SMF v2 - \r\n<strong>themes/default/index.template.php</strong>\r\n\r\nPaste the two lines immediately after <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag', 'Simple Machines Forum', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '357-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:37:51', '2013-09-24 07:37:51', '', 357, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/357-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4819, 1, '2013-09-24 07:38:39', '2013-09-24 07:38:39', 'Add the copied code into your Skadate <strong>Layout.tpl</strong> file immediately after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag.\r\n\r\nThis file is generally present at <strong>/layout/Layout.tpl</strong>.', 'SkaDate', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:38:39', '2013-09-24 07:38:39', '', 13, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4820, 1, '2013-09-24 07:39:52', '2013-09-24 07:39:52', 'Login to <strong>Administration Panel</strong> and go to the <strong>Layout Manager</strong>. Select <strong>Site Header</strong> and add a new <strong>HTML Block</strong>.\r\n\r\nIn the text area add the copied code and save your Site Header.', 'SocialEngine v4', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:39:52', '2013-09-24 07:39:52', '', 36, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/36-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4821, 1, '2013-09-24 07:41:13', '2013-09-24 07:41:13', 'Login to your SocialEngine Administration (usually http://www.domain.com/admin)\r\n\r\nUnder the <strong>Layout Settings</strong> tab, select the <strong>HTML Templates</strong> option.\r\n\r\nNow under <strong>Header/Footer Templates</strong> select <strong>header_global.tpl</strong>.', 'SocialEngine v3', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '361-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:41:13', '2013-09-24 07:41:13', '', 361, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/361-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4822, 1, '2013-09-24 07:58:40', '2013-09-24 07:58:40', 'Add the copied code in your <strong>default.master.php</strong> file immediately after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag.\r\n\r\nThis file is generally present at <strong>/applications/dashboard/views/default.master.php</strong>', 'Vanilla Forums', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '363-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:58:40', '2013-09-24 07:58:40', '', 363, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/363-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4823, 1, '2013-09-24 07:59:46', '2013-09-24 07:59:46', 'Login to your vBulletin Admin Control Panel (usually http://www.domain.com/forums/admincp)\r\n\r\nUnder the <strong>Styles &amp; Templates</strong> tab, select the <strong>Style Manager</strong> option.\r\n\r\nNow select the style in which you want to add the bar, and click on the <strong>Go</strong> button.\r\n\r\nIn the header textbox add the copied code at the beginning.', 'vBulletin', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 07:59:46', '2013-09-24 07:59:46', '', 17, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4824, 1, '2013-09-24 08:00:41', '2013-09-24 08:00:41', 'Edit the file <strong>/templates/webby2/header.tpl</strong> and paste the copied code just after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag.', 'vldPersonals', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '543-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 08:00:41', '2013-09-24 08:00:41', '', 543, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/543-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4825, 1, '2013-09-24 08:01:41', '2013-09-24 08:01:41', 'Your header file should be <strong>/templates/header.tpl</strong>. Edit the file using any text editor.\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	\r\n	', 'Woltlab', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3981-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 08:01:41', '2013-09-24 08:01:41', '', 3981, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/3981-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4826, 1, '2013-09-24 08:02:34', '2013-09-24 08:02:34', 'Login to WordPress Administration and go to <strong>Appearances</strong> -&gt; <strong>Editor</strong>. \r\n\r\nClick on <strong>Header (header.php)</strong> from the right side panel to edit the header.\r\n\r\nImmediately after the opening head tag add the copied code:\r\n<pre><code>&lt;head&gt;\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n	', 'WordPress', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 08:02:34', '2013-09-24 08:02:34', '', 29, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/29-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4827, 1, '2013-09-24 08:03:17', '2013-09-24 08:03:17', 'Insert the copied code into the Xoops <strong>theme.html</strong> file immediately after the <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag.\r\n\r\nThis file is generally present at <strong>/themes/default/theme.html</strong>', 'Xoops', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '369-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 08:03:17', '2013-09-24 08:03:17', '', 369, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/369-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4828, 1, '2013-09-24 08:04:27', '2013-09-24 08:04:27', 'Login to xenForo administration control panel and click on the <strong>Appearance</strong> tab.\r\n\r\nSelect <strong>Templates</strong> and search for <strong>PAGE_CONTAINER</strong> and open it for editing.\r\n\r\nPaste the copied code immediately after <code>&lt;head&gt;</code> tag and save your settings.', 'xenForo', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '367-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-24 08:04:27', '2013-09-24 08:04:27', '', 367, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/24/367-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4829, 1, '2013-09-25 03:41:08', '2013-09-25 03:41:08', '<h4>Selecting between Google and Microsoft</h4>\n\nCometChat''s real-time translate feature can integrate with either Microsoft''s Translate API or Google''s Translate API. Below are the pricing details for each service:\n\n<a href="http://go.microsoft.com/?linkid=9782667" target="_blank">Microsoft''s Translate API</a> (includes free plan)\n\n<a href="http://code.google.com/apis/language/translate/v2/pricing.html" target="_blank">Google''s Translate API</a> (only $20 for 1 million characters)\n\nOnce you have decided which API you would like to use, please follow the instructions accordingly:\n\n<h4>Configuring Microsoft''s Translate API</h4>\n\nYou need to sign up for the <strong>Microsoft Translator</strong> service. Depending on your requirements, you can select a <strong>Subscription</strong>.\n\n<a href="http://go.microsoft.com/?linkid=9782667" target="_blank">Microsoft''s Translate API</a> \n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2011/11/21-300x214.png" alt="21" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4830" />\n\nAfter completing the signup, you need to register your application at <a href="https://datamarket.azure.com/developer/applications/" target="_blank">https://datamarket.azure.com/developer/applications/</a>\n\nMake sure that your Client ID and Client Secret are unique values. Sample information:\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2011/11/22-300x239.png" alt="22" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4831" />\n\nOnce this is done, you need to configure the module.\n\nGo to <strong>CometChat Administration Panel</strong> --> <strong>Modules</strong> --> <strong>Real-time Translate</strong> --> <strong>config</strong>\n\nEnter your <strong>Client ID</strong> and <strong>Client Secret</strong> values which you filled earlier. Finally click on <strong>Update Settings</strong> button.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2011/11/23-300x222.png" alt="23" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4832" />\n\nThen simply clear your browser cache and test the real-time translate feature with another user.\n\n<h4>Configuring Google''s Translate API</h4>\n\nYou need to sign up for the <strong>Translate API</strong> service.\n\n<a href="https://code.google.com/apis/console" target="_blank">Google''s Translate API Signup</a>\n\nOn login, go to the <strong>Services</strong> tab and activate <strong>Translate API</strong>\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2011/11/24-300x227.png" alt="24" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4833" />\n\nNow, go to the <strong>Billng</strong> tab and make sure billing is enabled. Without adding this information, Google Translate will not work.\n\nGo to the <strong>API access</strong> tab and copy the <strong>API key</strong> from the <strong>Simple API Access</strong> section.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2011/11/25-300x112.png" alt="25" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4834" />\n\nGo to <strong>CometChat Administration Panel</strong> --> <strong>Modules</strong> --> <strong>Real-time Translate</strong> --> <strong>config</strong>\n\nLeave the <strong>Client ID</strong> and <strong>Client Secret</strong> values as blank, set <strong>Use Google Translate API</strong> to <strong>Yes</strong> and add the key which you copied earlier. Finally click on <strong>Update Settings</strong> button.\n\n<a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2011/11/26.png"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2011/11/26-288x300.png" alt="26" width="288" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4835" /></a>![Real-time Translate Settings](http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/media/26.png)\n\nThen simply clear your browser cache and test the real-time translate feature with another user.', 'Real-time Translate', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '585-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 03:41:08', '2013-09-25 03:41:08', '', 585, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/25/585-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
