\n* Click on the <strong>Update Settings</strong> button and close the window.	\r\n		\r\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/03/broadcast_2-288x300.png" alt="broadcast_2"  class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4341" />', 'RED5 or FMS (RTMP)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4298-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 04:19:33', '2013-09-25 04:19:33', '', 4298, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/25/4298-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4851, 1, '2013-09-25 04:21:57', '2013-09-25 04:21:57', '* Point your browser to the following URL: <strong>https://developer.addlive.com/cometchat</strong> or click on the link in the plugin setting window to create an AddLive account if you don’t have an Application ID and an Application Auth Secret key	\n\n* Register on the site with the required details		\n\n* Once you are done with the registration process, you will receive a mail from AddLive containing the Application ID and Stable API key	\n\n* Now place these values in plugin setting window and click on the <strong>Update</strong> settings	\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/03/addlive_full-300x295.png" alt="addlive_full" width="300" height="295" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4231" /></a>![AddLive](http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/03/addlive_full.png)', 'AddLive', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4225-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 04:21:57', '2013-09-25 04:21:57', '', 4225, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/25/4225-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4852, 1, '2013-09-25 04:22:03', '2013-09-25 04:22:03', '* Point your browser to the following URL: <strong>https://developer.addlive.com/cometchat</strong> or click on the link in the plugin setting window to create an AddLive account if you don’t have an Application ID and an Application Auth Secret key	\r\n\r\n* Register on the site with the required details		\r\n\r\n* Once you are done with the registration process, you will receive a mail from AddLive containing the Application ID and Stable API key	\r\n\r\n* Now place these values in plugin setting window and click on the <strong>Update</strong> settings	\r\n\r\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2013/03/addlive_full-300x295.png" alt="addlive_full"  class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-4231" />', 'AddLive', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4225-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 04:22:03', '2013-09-25 04:22:03', '', 4225, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/25/4225-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4853, 1, '2013-09-25 04:23:28', '2013-09-25 04:23:28', '<strong>Runs from our servers. No special software is required. Use of this technology/option is absolutely free and recommended.</strong>\n\nTo use this server select <strong>CometChat server</strong> from the <strong>Technology Dropdown box</strong>. Set the Video width and height accordingly and click on the <strong>Update Settings</strong> button.\n\n<a href="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/06/cometchat+server-e1339765666444.png"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/06/cometchat+server-e1339765666444-300x212.png" alt="cometchat+server" width="300" height="212" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2887" /></a>![CometChat Server]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/06/.png)', 'CometChat Server', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2939-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 04:23:28', '2013-09-25 04:23:28', '', 2939, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/25/2939-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4854, 1, '2013-09-25 04:23:51', '2013-09-25 04:23:51', '<strong>Runs from our servers. No special software is required. Use of this technology/option is absolutely free and recommended.</strong>\r\n\r\nTo use this server select <strong>CometChat server</strong> from the <strong>Technology Dropdown box</strong>. Set the Video width and height accordingly and click on the <strong>Update Settings</strong> button.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/06/cometchat+server-e1339765666444-300x212.png" alt="cometchat+server" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2887" />', 'CometChat Server', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2939-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 04:23:51', '2013-09-25 04:23:51', '', 2939, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/25/2939-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4855, 1, '2013-09-25 04:34:32', '2013-09-25 04:34:32', 'If you would like to self-host Adobe FMS server,\n\n* Purchase, download and install Adobe FMS on your server (outside support scope)\n\nIf you would like to use a third-party Adobe FMS host,\n\n* Sign up with a host like <a href="http://www.influxis.com/" target="_blank">http://www.influxis.com/</a>\n\n#Installing Audio/Video Chat Plugin with FMS\n\nCreate a folder named <strong>''avchat''</strong> in the applications directory of your FMS.	\n		\nFor example, if you are using FMS v4.5 on windows system then you need to create the <strong>avchat</strong> folder in <strong>''C:Program FilesAdobeFlash Media Server 4.5applications''</strong> folder.\n\n<h4>Configuring the Audio/Video Chat Plugin</h4>\n\n* In the <strong>CometChat Admin Panel</strong> -&gt; <strong>Plugins</strong> section, add the <strong>Audio/Video Chat Plugin</strong> to your live plugins and click on the <strong>config</strong> link besides the name.\n	\n* Enter the required details.	\n		\n* Click on the <strong>Update Settings</strong> button and close the window.\n\n![Configuring the plugin]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/06/.png)', 'FMS (RTMFP)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2954-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 04:34:32', '2013-09-25 04:34:32', '', 2954, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/25/2954-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4856, 1, '2013-09-25 04:35:00', '2013-09-25 04:35:00', 'If you would like to self-host Adobe FMS server,\r\n\r\n* Purchase, download and install Adobe FMS on your server (outside support scope)\r\n\r\nIf you would like to use a third-party Adobe FMS host,\r\n\r\n* Sign up with a host like <a href="http://www.influxis.com/" target="_blank">http://www.influxis.com/</a>\r\n\r\n#Installing Audio/Video Chat Plugin with FMS\r\n\r\nCreate a folder named <strong>''avchat''</strong> in the applications directory of your FMS.	\r\n		\r\nFor example, if you are using FMS v4.5 on windows system then you need to create the <strong>avchat</strong> folder in <strong>''C:Program FilesAdobeFlash Media Server 4.5applications''</strong> folder.\r\n\r\n<h4>Configuring the Audio/Video Chat Plugin</h4>\r\n\r\n* In the <strong>CometChat Admin Panel</strong> -&gt; <strong>Plugins</strong> section, add the <strong>Audio/Video Chat Plugin</strong> to your live plugins and click on the <strong>config</strong> link besides the name.\r\n	\r\n* Enter the required details.	\r\n		\r\n* Click on the <strong>Update Settings</strong> button and close the window.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2012/06/FMS1-e1339765891339-279x300.png" alt="FMS" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2889" />', 'FMS (RTMFP)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2954-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-25 04:35:00', '2013-09-25 04:35:00', '', 2954, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/documentation/2013/09/25/2954-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
