(177, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>Most Popular</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/facebook/''>Facebook</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=facebook&amp;_wpnonce=76fa2939a4&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Facebook''>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>Add Facebook social plugins and the ability to publish new posts to a Facebook Timeline or Facebook Page. Official Facebook plugin.</p>\n<h4>Newest Plugins</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/duracelltomi-google-tag-manager/''>DuracellTomi&#039;s Google Tag Manager for WordPress</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=duracelltomi-google-tag-manager&amp;_wpnonce=1251b13308&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''DuracellTomi&#039;s Google Tag Manager for WordPress''>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>The first Google Tag Manager plugin for WordPress with business goals in mind.</p>\n', 'no'),
